General.Name: Compass Digital Acquisition Corp. Warrant
General.Description: Compass Digital Acquisition Corp. intends to effect a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to focus its search on companies in the technology sectors, including in the technology led digital transformation software and services sector. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Dallas, Texas.
